  abilityName: Destinous Sigil
  description: 'At sunset, etch a cosmic rune somewhere

    secret on your person.

    Choose
    a number. When a die rolls that

    number you may adjust it to any other value

    on
    that die. This can be performed a number

    of times equal to the chosen number.

    A
    different number is chosen next sunset.'
